{"tid":2040153,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀中文既入！上網考final有條唔識做！","createTime":"2020-05-28T11:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T02:18:37.000Z","uid":215620,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb747f3c9a6fcfb8b54a791e1ac9d34574dc62a","tid":2040153,"uid":215620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"《子產告范宣子輕幣》一文入面，用咗幾多詞類活用，可唔可以幫手list曬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2316ca607da966e51a5dce1358c56ceab0c6a82","tid":2040153,"uid":52793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:36:12.000Z","msg":"現代漢語?"},{"pid":"e762a8cc444d7379e1173f1b3be68a11264c5e4f","tid":2040153,"uid":180707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"動詞<br />\n名詞<br />\n主語<br />\n謂語<br />\n幫到盡啦"},{"pid":"9faae7165a705187839ba7d3586fa5a5d6dbe270","tid":2040153,"uid":215620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"範宣子爲政，諸侯之幣重，鄭人病之。<br />\n二月，鄭伯如晉。子產寓書於子西，以告宣子，曰：&ldquo;子爲晉國，四鄰諸侯，不聞令德而聞重幣。僑也惑之。僑聞君子長國家者，非無賄之患，而無令名之難，夫諸侯之賄，聚於公室，則諸侯貳；若吾子賴之，則晉國貳。諸侯貳則晉國壞，晉國貳則子之家壞。何沒沒也？將焉用賄？<br />\n夫令名，德之輿也。德，國家之基也。有基無壞，無亦是務乎？有德則樂，樂則能久。詩云：&lsquo;樂只君子，邦家之基。&rsquo;有令德也夫！&lsquo;上帝臨女，無貳爾心。&rsquo;有令名也夫！恕思以明德，則令名載而行之，是以遠至邇安。毋寧使人謂子，子實生我，而謂子浚我以生乎？象有齒以焚其身，賄也。&rdquo;<br />\n宣子說，乃輕幣。<br />\n<br />\n原文係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條題係要講清楚邊句用咗d乜野詞類活用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363a255c77e3882ef1ae21c8cac3c800bf959d0a","tid":2040153,"uid":356462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"我都考梗，一齊做？"},{"pid":"c4d04cf9b90eaf02a717e512d1b69c5c0e931935","tid":2040153,"uid":356462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quo